sequenceDiagram
accTitle: Mermaid return semantics
accDescr {
Demonstrates solid Mermaid messages mapping to sequencer calls and dotted Mermaid messages mapping to sequencer returns.
From the project root, regenerate this Mermaid transform and SVG with:
node sequencer.js --mermaid -i test/mermaid-features/08-return-semantics/input.mmd -o -f -t test/mermaid-features/08-return-semantics
}
participant Caller
participant Service
Caller->>Service: Request [Mermaid: Caller->>Service: Request]
Service-->>Caller: Response [Mermaid: Service-->>Caller: Response]
Service--)Caller: Async-style open return [Mermaid: Service--)Caller: Async-style open return]
Service--xCaller: Failure return [Mermaid: Service--xCaller: Failure return]
Service-->Caller: Completion without arrow [Mermaid: Service-->Caller: Completion without arrow]
